# Local machine config — never commit
local.properties
dev.properties

# Signing — never commit. keystore.properties holds the store/key passwords in plain text, so it is
# every bit as sensitive as the keystore itself, and so is any archive made to back the two up.
# A keystore.zip sitting here nearly got committed on 2026-07-22; match the whole family, not just
# the two filenames we happened to think of.
*.keystore
*.jks
*.p12
*.bks
keystore*
lector-release*

